name: Prototype
body:
### How to Start a Prototype

1. Install [Node](https://nodejs.org/en/)
2. Open PowerShell (Windows) or Terminal (Mac)
3. Install Harp
`npm install -g harp`
4. Setup a new prototype project
`harp init my-project-name -b nformux/prototype-boilerplate`
